            "verse": 5,
            "text": "and the mountains like colorful carded wool"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "On that Day, he whose scale of good deeds is heavy"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "shall live a pleasant luxurious life"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "But he whose scale of good deeds is light"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "shall abode in Haviah"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "and what will explain to you, what it (Haviah) is"
